<h3>Travel information</h3>
<p><strong>Tees Valley Hospital is within easy reach of the A19 and A66 and a 15 minute taxi ride from Middlesbrough Railway Station.</strong><br/><br/></p><br/><p><strong>From the A19 North</strong><br/>Take the A1130 exit towards Acklam. At the roundabout take the third exit onto the A1130. At the roundabout take the second exit onto Mandale Road/A1130. Turn right onto Acklam Road/A1032. Turn left onto Church Lane.</p><br/><p><strong>From the A19 South</strong><br/>Take the A1130 exit towards Acklam. At the roundabout take the first exit onto the A1130. At the roundabout take the second exit onto Mandale Road/A1130. Turn right on to Acklam Road/A1032. Turn left onto Church Lane.</p><br/><p>Â </p>
